commits.message: feat(hop): expand amount of anchor keys
Zip_extract app, exe file for the todo app

Refactor background scripts and enhance logging functionality

- Updated event listener handling in extcomms.ts for improved clarity and consistency.
- Modified package.json to streamline development scripts and added 'concurrently' dependency.
- Enhanced tab management in background/index.ts to ensure proper focus and reload behavior.
- Improved error handling and logging in various components, including tab tracking and storage functions.
- Cleaned up unused imports and added checks for document readiness in DiagnosticLogger.
- Updated SpeechEditor component to clarify permission prompts and improve user experience.
Set up virtual environment and loaded packages
